The "Calculator" program is a simple, easy-to-use, program written by: Techman749. 
It's pretty self-explanatory, meaning that it does what it's name says. 
It can do addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.
to re-enter the program just type "calculator" (The program exits after you enter a problem.) in your utilities folder to run it. 
You also MUST be in your utilities folder to access the program. 
Just type "utilities" and then type "calculator" to run the program
